    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work to be roadworthy. The engine runs roughly and the transmission slips frequently, indicating a need for major repairs or a complete overhaul. The body shows heavy wear with several large dents and patches of rust, and the interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery. It is recommended for a buyer looking for a serious project or a donor vehicle for parts.",
